<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171894>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Selfcoelum limnodromi n. gen., n. sp. from the long­billed dowitcher, Limnodromus scolopaceus. 1. Ventral view of adult. 2. Composite drawing of anterior end showing placement of the genital pore and terminal genitalia, ventral view. 3. Composite drawing of female genitalia, dorsal view. Abbreviations: C, cecum; O, ovary; S, seminal vesicle; T, testis; U, uterus; V, vitelline follicles. Scale bars: 1, 2,050 µm; 2, 550 µm; 3, 1,200 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171894/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

